### Azure Virtual Machine

The Ubuntu Linux virtual machine was created in Microsoft Azure and configured as the cloud server for this project.





## Live Website

The Cybersecurity Awareness website successfully deployed and accessible through the DNS hostname.


## SSH Remote Access

SSH was used to securely connect to the Azure virtual machine for server administration and file management.


## Custom Bash Script 

The custome serverinfo.sh script displays server health information including uptime, disk usage and memory usage.

